Sculptor->Load

The first selection in the "Sculptor" menu is "Load". This option is
simular to the "Open" option in "File", except that it is used to load
object and scene files into the MOVIEOLA environment.. The default
file path is the project scene folder, but the user may use the file
selector to choose another path. The file may be in anyof the
supported formats (listed in the Sculptor Save menu). If the file
contains one or more objects, all the objects are added to the current
scene. If the file contains a scene, all the objects and lights are
added to the current scene.
